{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01WP33HNh8L5SMmMuL7Xnpbw","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Looking at the problem: Find max of f(x) = x³ - 3x where x⁴ + 36 ≤ 13x².\n\nLet me solve it mathematically:\n- x⁴ - 13x² + 36 ≤ 0 → (x²-4)(x²-9) ≤ 0 → 4 ≤ x² ≤ 9 → x ∈ [-3,-2] ∪ [2,3]\n- f'(x) = 3x²-3 > 0 in this domain, so f is monotonic\n- Max on [2,3] is f(3) = 18; max on [-3,-2] is f(-2) = -2\n- Answer: **18**\n\nKey identity: x³ - 3x - 18 = (x-3)(x² + 3x + 6), and x² + 3x + 6 = (x+3/2)² + 15/4 > 0."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":243,"cache_read_input_tokens":26659,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":243},"output_tokens":115,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9884d695-d02f-46b9-ac2e-75d92eb01e49","uuid":"5761e508-f705-4a16-a67f-416bbf1e3135"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01WP33HNh8L5SMmMuL7Xnpbw","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01YBaStF32X4mkMoLEb386J5","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/private/var/folders/pl/c57pb2_52t513h0r4dgr0ryc0000gn/T/exp_1986_A1__A__r0_6qr7lvvc/workspace/Solution.lean","content":"import Mathlib\n\nnoncomputable def putnam_1986_a1_solution : ℝ := 18\n\ntheorem putnam_1986_a1 :\n    IsGreatest {y : ℝ | ∃ x : ℝ, x^4 + 36 ≤ 13 * x^2 ∧ y = x^3 - 3*x} putnam_1986_a1_solution := by\n  constructor\n  · refine ⟨3, ?_, ?_⟩\n    · norm_num\n    · show (putnam_1986_a1_solution : ℝ) = 3^3 - 3*3\n      unfold putnam_1986_a1_solution\n      norm_num\n  · rintro y ⟨x, hx, rfl⟩\n    have h1 : x^2 ≤ 9 := by nlinarith [sq_nonneg (x^2 - 9), hx]\n    have h2 : x ≤ 3 := by nlinarith [sq_nonneg (x - 3), h1]\n    have h3 : (0:ℝ) ≤ x^2 + 3*x + 6 := by nlinarith [sq_nonneg (2*x + 3)]\n    have h4 : (x - 3) * (x^2 + 3*x + 6) ≤ 0 :=\n      mul_nonpos_of_nonpos_of_nonneg (by linarith) h3\n    show x^3 - 3*x ≤ putnam_1986_a1_solution\n    unfold putnam_1986_a1_solution\n    nlinarith [h4]\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":243,"cache_read_input_tokens":26659,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":243},"output_tokens":115,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9884d695-d02f-46b9-ac2e-75d92eb01e49","uuid":"f98437d5-6bce-4efc-a22b-0795891ac5c1"}
